    EndActivity
    Represents the game end activity.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    FunctionCard
    Represents the function of a medication.
    GameActivity
    Represents the game activity in which the game is played.
    InfoDialog
    Represents the dialog with information about the game.
    MainActivity
    Represents the start menu which is opened when the application is launched.
    MedicationCard
    Represents the medication.
    SettingsActivity
    Represents the setting menu where the medication has to be chosen and new medication can be added.
